June 7, 1965. No. 14,

Original.

Louisiana v. Mississippi et al. [For earlier orders herein, see 375 U. S. 803, 950; 377 U. S. 901.]

The Report of the Special Master is received and ordered filed. Exceptions, if any, with supporting briefs, to the Report of the Special Master may be filed by the parties on or before August 25, 1965. Reply briefs, if any, to such exceptions may be filed on or before September 24, 1965.
